{
  "stem": "19441.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 523.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I was in the toilet, so here I drank and here I vomited.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I did that a few time, 'til it settled down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, girls, we have to eat it, because you are hungry, dehydrated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have to get used to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was our first welcome.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then there was nothing there in that room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the girls went--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was 600.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it's a huge room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they wanted to undress the coat and put it nicely together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, lie in the coat, because it's more-- you can't-- you will be cold and uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Have a look what I will do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I put the muff under my head and I lie in my coat, which had fur collar and fur [INAUDIBLE] and I put my hands in so I shouldn't be so cold.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I [INAUDIBLE] I saw that they are very naive and not practical.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They taking off the coat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, if here we lie, you will have coat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if not, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that's it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Next day, they [NON-ENGLISH], that means 'run, run, run,' beat us and-- so I said, girls, run so you wouldn't be hit.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they let us stand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And lot of girls collapse, fainted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For hours in the cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is-- they-- it wasn't the camp for that, for surviving.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just for suffering and for killing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they let us stand there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A lot of girls fainted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was another girl from city, Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was also a sport girl, so we two had made ourself the-- that they will carry the girls somewhere inside, in a barrack, so they should recover.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- we were standing, that's what I said.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
